IMXY      LLLLLLLLLLLLUUUUUUUUUUUU CCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCCC
IMXY:  Verb to determine pixel coordinates under cursor
          Only input is from TV cursor.
         @      Output adverbs
PIXXY    @    0.0         4096.0   Pixel location (X,Y,...) in
         @                         image.
TVBUT    @                         Value of button(s) pushed.
----------------------------------------------------------------
IMXY
Type: verb
Use:  Read a image pixel position using cursor, print position
      and store it as an adverb
Adverbs:
  No input adverbs

  Output adverbs
   PIXXY.....Pixel location (X,Y,...) in the image.
   TVBUT.....Value of button(s) pushed: 1, 2, 4, or 8 are likely
             but combinations may be possible.
